         Yeah you can kill stuff down there, or kill one of the sperms and get a candle (key for North) and solo in North wing.  Takes a little practice there and most mobs HT you, but if you can get a steady tempo going its very very nice experience, and its actually... NOT BORING!</P><P>If you have good gear you can go all the way through HS (have a lot of spare time on your hands lol) up to Drusella, who you'd have a tough time soloing.  Dunno if anyone has ever done it before, but the rest of the zone is doable with the right skill and equipment, and time.</P><P>Daedrea Darksoul<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
